message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely category as it deals with audio signal processing and source separation. cs.LG is also likely as it deals with machine learning models. cs.SI is another possible category as it deals with signal processing and neural networks. cs.NE is also possible as it deals with neural networks. cs.CV is less likely as it deals with computer vision, but it is still possible as the paper may use image processing techniques for spectrogram analysis.
